c: 2
v: 109
t: "Ne abaanji abandu beshitabu bekomba muno okhubakalusia inyuma nimumalile okhusuubila mube abakhayi khulweyishinda okhurula mumioyo chiabu, obwatoto nibumalile okhuboolela, kho leshelane mulalingakhwo tawe okhuula shinga Nyasaye aletsa nende okhubusia khukhwe, Toto Nyasaye nomunyali wabuli eshindu"